----[ Purpose

    This plugin allows Cacti Administrators to log user change activity

----[ Features

    Log all $_POST activities to the Cacti Server that can change the contents of the system.
	
----[ Installation

    Install just like any other plugin, just throw it in the plugin directory,
    and Install and Enabled from the Plugin Management Interface.

    Once this is done, you have to goto Configuration -> Settings -> Misc and define data retention
	and turn on auditing.
    
----[ Possible Bugs?
   
    If you figure out this problem, see the Cacti forums!

----[ Future Changes
    
    Got any ideas or complaints, please log an issue on GitHub.

